@abhisekp Added some styles to your button: 

.randomize {
  cursor: pointer;
  background:transparent;
  border:2px solid #bbb;
  padding:1em 2em;
  border-radius:20px;
  color:rgba(0,0,0,.7);
  text-transform:uppercase;
  font-size:10px;
  font-weight:800;
  letter-spacing:2px;
}
.randomize:hover {
  background:royalblue;
  border:2px solid royalblue;
  color:rgba(255,255,255,1);
}
